0182   0000             OldPlayerShipLSB       .EQU $43E1       ;Old LSB screen ram: Upper left character of player ship
0183   0000             PlayerShipMSB          .EQU $43E2       ;MSB screen ram: Upper left character of player ship
0184   0000             PlayerShipLSB          .EQU $43E3       ;LSB screen ram: Upper left character of player ship
