6090   301A 30 28                              .DW L3028 ; if Counter93 is 1
6091   301C 30 BA                              .DW L30BA ; if Counter93 is 2
6092   301E 31 24                              .DW L3124 ; if Counter93 is 3
6093   3020 31 5A                              .DW L315A ; if Counter93 is 4
6094   3022 31 B4                              .DW L31B4 ; if Counter93 is 5
6095   3024 32 2C                              .DW L322C ; if Counter93 is 6
6096   3026 30 12                              .DW L3012 ; if Counter93 is 7
6097   3028             
6098   3028             ; from jump table T3018 if Counter93 is 1.
6099   3028             ; Do the 'Angry movement pattern A/B' (pattern 26/28).
6100   3028             ; After that, the alien formation is further down on the screen.
